                        <interp inst="t18450707-name-355" type="given" value="CATHERINE"></interp>CATHERINE MERRITT</persName>
                  </hi>. The prisoner lodged in my house, and was apprehended on the 13th of June—I found two mustard-pots, a cork<lb></lb>screw, and other things, in the front kitchen adjoining my place, where the prisoner used to go—the prosecutor has identified these things.</p>
